        <div class="step"><div class="step-num">2</div><h3>Same-day visit</h3><p>For emergency repairs, we&rsquo;re on site same-day in most cases (Mon&ndash;Sat, Casey area). New installs: site measure within 48 hours.</p></div>
        <div class="step"><div class="step-num">3</div><h3>Fixed quote</h3><p>Written fixed-price quote &mdash; door, motor, install, removal of old door, all hardware. No surprise charges.</p></div>
        <div class="step"><div class="step-num">4</div><h3>Install / repair</h3><p>Repair: typically 60&ndash;90 minutes on site, one trip. New install: 3&ndash;5 hours single door, 1 day double. Old door removed and disposed of.</p></div>
        <div class="step"><div class="step-num">5</div><h3>Test &amp; handover</h3><p>30-cycle test, safety-sensor calibration, auto-reverse verification, app pairing for smart openers, manual-release demo. 5&ndash;10 year warranty.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
